I"¹
<p class="info"><strong>Note</strong>: The <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Content-Type</code> header should be set to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">application/json</code> along with the merchant API key</p>

<p class="success"><strong>Example request</strong></p>

<p>A curl request to request the cashier:</p>

