<p>A successful response will return an HTTP status code of <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">201</code> and have the following schema:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Field</th>
      <th>Type</th>
      <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>StatusCode</td>
      <td>string</td>
      <td>If an error is returned the error code is shown here</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>message</td>
      <td>string</td>
      <td>the CashierUrl or A message of the error</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
